# ⚙️ Installation

Clone repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/AI-Investment-Decision-Engine.git

Create environment:

python -m venv venv

Activate:

Windows:

venv\Scripts\activate

Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt
▶️ Run Application

Start Streamlit:

streamlit run app/app.py

The dashboard will open automatically.

